# Public Architecture

| Layer | Responsibility |
|-------|----------------|
| Edge Hardware | Acquisition of trusted industrial telemetry |
| Gateway | Secure ingestion and preprocessing |
| Verification | Integrity validation and evidence generation |
| Registry | Immutable registration of verifiable evidence |
| Audit | Independent verification and traceability |

