# Repository Scope

This repository presents the public research implementation of the PoWV Protocol.

To protect intellectual property and industrial partnerships, implementation-specific details are intentionally omitted, including:

- Production firmware
- Internal communication interfaces
- Proprietary validation logic
- Deployment architecture
- Industrial integrations
- Device provisioning procedures
- Production cryptographic material
